<h2>Everything DiSC Workplace <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em>Online</em></span> Certification</h2>
<h2>Investment -&nbsp;&pound;1,750.00 without Kit or&nbsp;&pound;2,495.00 with Kit</h2>
<p>As a facilitator, you need solutions that enhance your training sessions&nbsp;and guarantee the best experience for your learners. Everything DiSC&reg; builds better workplaces,&nbsp;and the opportunity to master its facilitation lies no further than your own computer with&nbsp;Everything DiSC Workplace&reg; Certification.</p>
<p>Designed with your busy schedule in mind, this facilitator certification course allows you the&nbsp;flexibility of self-paced learning, paired with live webinar sessions led by our expert trainers. All&nbsp;the content is interactive and memorable, so you have fun while you&rsquo;re learning! And our live&nbsp;instructor-led sessions allow you and your classmates to collaborate and share best practices.<br />Whether you are new to DiSC&reg; or have worked with it for years, you&rsquo;ll increase your confidence and competence&nbsp;in delivering Everything DiSC and explore challenging scenarios that can come your way.</p>
<p><strong>Release the power&nbsp;of Everything DiSC&mdash;learn about becoming a Certified Everything DiSC Workplace Facilitator today!</strong></p>
<p>This four week online course will give you an in-depth knowledge about Everything DiSC Workplace&reg; and the research behind it. It will blend self-directed learning with live collaborative sessions to help you gain expertise and confidence with Everything DiSC from the convenience of your nearest internet connection.</p>
<p>Because this course specifically focuses on Everything DiSC Workplace&reg;, you must own an Everything DiSC Workplace Facilitation Kit to participate in this course.</p>
