<h4>Overview:</h4>
<p>Self-directed learning and virtual collaborative sessions help participants gain the expertise and credentials needed to bring this powerful tool directly into their organisations.&nbsp;</p>
<h4>Description:</h4>
<p>Accessible anytime, from the privacy of the learner&rsquo;s home or office computer, Everything DiSC Workplace&reg; Certification training is just a click away. Blending self-directed learning with virtual instructor-led sessions, this online course takes participants for a deep dive into the theory and research behind Everything DiSC&reg;, including tips and techniques on how to use the research to address common questions, and hands-on practice using the resources available in the Everything DiSC Workplace&reg; Facilitation toolkit. Online work integrates a rich media experience with active, collaborative learning exercises to help participants apply DiSC&reg; concepts to current challenges in an engaging and meaningful way.</p>
<h4>Learner Take-Aways&nbsp;</h4>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Gain credentials to conduct Everything DiSC Workplace&reg; sessions in an organisation</li>
<li>Experience first-hand the Everything DiSC Workplace assessment and apply the personalised profile results to real-world scenarios</li>
<li>Develop expertise working with the Everything DiSC Workplace&reg; Facilitation toolkit&nbsp;</li>
<li>Upon successful completion of the course, receive the credential of Everything DiSC Workplace&reg; Certified Trainer</li>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
<h4>Programme Components</h4>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Four modules of self-directed and live collaborative learning (each requiring three to five hours of time per week), conducted over a four week period</li>
<li>Periodic knowledge checks to help participants assess how well they understand the content and to improve learning and retention</li>
<li>Final Certification exam (self-directed/graded activity)</li>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
