<h4>Pre-Requisites</h4>
<p>To be eligible to register, you must</p>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Own an Everything DiSC Workplace Facilitation Kit</li>
<li>Be able to commit to four weeks of self-directed work</li>
<li>Be able to attend ALL four live collaborative (instructor-led) sessions</li>
<li>Be able to access the course from a personal computer and use a mobile phone or land line for the live collaborative sessions&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
<h4>Time Commitment</h4>
<p>This online course consists of four modules over a four week period. You will complete one module per week. Each module will require three to five hours of time per week, broken down in the following way</p>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>One to three hours of self-directed online work, to be completed before the module&rsquo;s live collaborative (instructor-led webinar) session</li>
<li>One 90-minute live collaborative (instructor-led webinar) session per week (NOTE: Attendance is required at ALL live collaborative sessions)</li>
<li>30 to 60 minutes of additional self-directed online work following the live collaborative session</li>
<li>A final exam, to be completed within 48 hours of the final live collaborative session</li>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
